WELCOME!!!

To build executable file: gcc -o zaidishell zaidishell.c

To run executable file: ./zaidishell

For piping: command | command

For redirection: command < file > file

For changing directory:  cd PATHNAME (It does allow relative and absolute path)

For clearing shell: clear

For exiting shell: exit

For getting help about commands: help

For seeing current directory: pwd

For listing files: ls

For creating background process: &

for seeing all background processes: jobs

For killing background process: kill PID

For seeing history: history

To go back in path: cd ..

To print in shell: echo

To make file: touch filename

To view file in shell: cat filename


